            <h2 class="section-title">Welcome to My World</h2>
            <p>Hello! My name is Abel, and I'm a 17-year-old from Ethiopia. I'm a Grade 10 student with a deep passion for math and science. This website is a place where I explore the wonders of these subjects and share my curiosity with the world.</p>
